Keep optimal health: Veggies and fruits capsules can be used as a daily supplement to enhance your overall health and wellness. Rich in vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants, they can help support a healthy immune system. But not only that - these capsules can also help promote better sleep. The nutrients found in fruits and vegetables, such as magnesium, potassium and tryptophan, have been shown to help promote relaxation, leading to improved sleep quality and greater energy and vitality

Made in USA: We take pride in creating high-quality health supplements that people can trust. That's why our Veggies and Fruits Capsules are made in a GMP certified facility, with strict quality standards. The designer of the capsules is one of the top nutritionists in the United States

Suitable for kids to seniors: Horjoy Veggies and Fruits Capsules are perfect for all ages, from kids to seniors. These capsules are made with all-natural ingredients that are free from added sugars, fillers, preservatives and synthetics, making them safe and healthy for everyone. They are also easy to swallow, and won't leave a bad taste in your mouth. They are a great alternative for those who don't like or have issues consuming fresh fruits and vegetables

After-sales service: We offer a 30-day satisfaction guarantee. If you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, please contact us and we will do our best to address any issues and make things right for you

reviews.reviewerName: I recently started incorporating Horjoy Veggies and Fruits Supplements into my daily routine, and I couldn't be happier with the results. These supplements have truly become a game-changer for me, and I'm excited to share my positive experience with others.  First and foremost, the quality of Horjoy's supplements is exceptional. It's evident that they source the finest ingredients, as I can taste the freshness and purity in every capsule. Knowing that I'm getting a concentrated dose of essential vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants from real fruits and vegetables is reassuring, especially when my busy schedule doesn't always allow for a well-balanced diet.  One of the standout features of these supplements is their convenience. Life can get hectic, and it's not always easy to prepare and consume a variety of fruits and vegetables every day. Horjoy Veggies and Fruits Supplements simplify this process by providing a quick and efficient way to ensure I'm meeting my nutritional needs. Plus, there's no need to worry about spoilage or waste, as these capsules have a long shelf life.  Since I started taking these supplements, I've noticed a significant improvement in my overall well-being. I have more energy throughout the day, and I feel more alert and focused. My immune system also seems to be stronger, as I've experienced fewer colds and illnesses since incorporating Horjoy's supplements into my daily regimen.  The best part is that these supplements are gentle on the stomach and don't cause any digestive discomfort, which can sometimes be an issue with other vitamin and mineral products. I appreciate that they are suitable for people with dietary restrictions, as they are gluten-free, vegan, and free from artificial additives.  In addition to the physical benefits, I've also noticed an improvement in my skin's complexion and overall glow. The antioxidants in these supplements are doing wonders for my skin's health, and I couldn't be happier with the radiant results.  Overall, I wholeheartedly recommend Horjoy Veggies and Fruits Supplements to anyone looking to enhance their nutrition and overall well-being. These supplements have made a noticeable difference in my life, and I'm confident they can do the same for others. With Horjoy, you can invest in your health with peace of mind, knowing you're getting a top-notch product that delivers real results.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to swallow and less expensive than others
reviews.reviewText: I've taken these supplements for about a year and a half now. Like almost everyone leaving a review here, I don't get nearly enough fruits and veggies in my daily diet, and i know how important it is for my health to do so. These diet supplements appeal to me because they're an easy way to get my fruits and veggies, and they're pure fruits and veggies, nothing else (except for the capsule casing). Also, the price for the Horjoy supplements is much less than its most well-known competitor. I can't say for sure it increases my energy level or makes aches and pains go away faster, or whatever customers claim it does. I'm a 67 year old male who's in great health and is active in sporting activities. These days I rarely if ever get headaches, constipation or diarrhea, and I don't have significant aches and pains that usually come with advanced age. Like I said, I can't attribute these with 100% certainty to the Horjoy pills, but I'm reasonably sure they're a benefit to me regardless.

reviews.reviewTitle: Very good for health but are stucking in the larynx.
reviews.reviewText: I am very happy with the Fruits and Veggies Supplement. They are definitely do their job.The only thing that I would really improve is the plastic coating of those pills. Unlike any other pills I taken those ones are sticking in the larynx after swallowing them. I figured out to take them with lots of water / drink otherwise they just stuck between the throat and the stomach in the larynx... Not a good feeling for quite a while and when trying to eat something like bread to "push" them down... it sometimes heart quite a lot.
